                            <comment id="16417585" author="tilman" created="Wed, 28 Mar 2018 15:48:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;You&apos;re right, I&apos;ll add a getter and setter and pass to PDFRenderer.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
